metadata.name: Love Story Unicorns #1
metadata.description: Love Story Unicorns is a collection of 10,000 unique Unicorn NFTs - unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Unicorn doubles as your Love Story membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to at least X2 sessions a year with a Relationship Expert and 1 tree planted for every Unicorn minted in our wholesome community. Future perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation. Visit www.LoveStoryUnicorns.com for more details.
